{"tid":462896,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：公務員學院將有認識中國課程","createTime":"2017-11-09T03:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T04:01:37.000Z","uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b791f2f03b66e6177a99ce359c806fc823a37033","tid":462896,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:50:03.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥接受香港電台節目《議事論事》專訪時表示，公務員學院將會有認識中國的課程。 林鄭月娥早前宣讀施政報告，提到政府將建立公務員學院，被本台記者提問質疑是否將公務員洗腦。林鄭在港台訪問中提到公務員學院，指香港主權移交20年，公務員需要從憲制上更加了解一國兩制，將成立的公務員學院，除了為公務員提供創新科技和公共參與等培訓外，亦會有認識中國的課程。 對於英治時期已有的中央政策組，林鄭將會改其名為政策創新與統籌辦事處，她聲言是為了改變以往予人政府部門不協作的垢病，藉特首的統籌，給各部門外在力量的衝擊，促進協作。 <br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-09-2017/42449\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F11-09-2017%2F42449&d=Ye4xvbTKLIGs6GZxb87OXwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=f9797ebd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-09-2017/42449</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2017"},{"pid":"52459c671aaee89ab3ed782ef6f90dd350f61a09","tid":462896,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:55:42.000Z","msg":"公務員政治不再中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a91aa38f4375da98a4407617da353af2e80bf9","tid":462896,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:55:49.000Z","msg":"唔撚駛啦,我AL 讀中史,己經知道中共幾咁黑暗,老毛幾咁ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591e5fc1e30c7acd34dc1dab23dceb5942c9360c","tid":462896,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:57:20.000Z","msg":"中央幹部分校？"},{"pid":"4d707e09d43a1f269656fce35bc0b5e98f0c95da","tid":462896,"uid":68352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:01:37.000Z","msg":"正呀 唔洗返工去上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}